<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-11-19T17:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-11-19T17:00:00-05:00" n="231" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d231">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">763.72119/2621: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Ambassador in Brazil</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_MEV1" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Morgan</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                                </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-11-19T17:00:00-05:00">November 19, 1918—5 p.m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Your November 15, 1 p.m. Department feels that it is not essential for
                            Brazil to be represented at the preliminary conferences. Please say to
                                <persName corresp="#p_DGD1">Da Gama</persName> that Department
                            considers it desirable that he should go to the peace conference and
                            wishes to advise him for his very confidential information that it
                            understands that the peace conference will probably meet in the middle
                            of the month of January next.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                                </persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>